{"id":"defad4bc-b447-4a5d-baed-8088c9e6b9f0","name":"Fish","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><strong>Fish moves through pipes to hide in empty motel rooms.</strong><br><br><strong>Tonight, there aren't any.</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AiU7IdEg5F6P5zQPo5mmd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p></p><hr><p></p><p></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span></h1><p></p><p>You've just arrived at a cheap motel (The Wayfinder Motel) and rented the final unoccupied room, but this motel has a secret that everyone pretends doesn't exist. Fish is a creature that travels through the pipes of the motel and lives in the bathtubs of unoccupied rooms. Tonight, that's not an option.</p><p>Fish has some questions for you. She enjoys hearing people admit to terrible things they've done in their lives. You should answer honestly. Maybe fun stuff will happen.<strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">Mysophilia, gross, breath, scary, smell, stench, water, kink</span></p><hr><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/d2F5aW25gFac5-0DegvGg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p></p><p></p><hr><p></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Notes</strong></span></h1><p></p><ul><li><p>Extremely gross. Potential for violence and noncon.</p></li><li><p>If you want a slightly different experience, try simply going to sleep without acknowledging her.</p></li><li><p>Feel free to chat with Helena, the receptionist.</p></li><li><p>Bonus art <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fo/385q7sruvy9aqwgclxl8w/AAQBTBSeWkKC1CunpEtZI7I?rlkey=0vwpe8kpoyypalikbwfbhf1av&amp;st=a5hkpszk&amp;dl=0\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9Ou9zYIMIWIBP2RGnwukQ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Intros</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Intro 1 - User arrives alone to the motel room</p><p>Intro 2 - Helena is playing with Fish, expecting User's check-in time to be later.</p><p>Intro 3 - Helena bursts into the hotel room, expecting it to be empty.</p><p></p><hr><p></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/V3gqnrthc5cCP5RT9t0kh.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p></p><hr><p></p><p></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Wayfinder Motel is a Series!</strong></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Playable in any order.</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b29c9ac1-3e34-4d07-9246-81986b4eb793_character-helena-monsterfucker-receptionist\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 149, 255);\">Helena</span></a> is the receptionist</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/defad4bc-b447-4a5d-baed-8088c9e6b9f0_character-fish\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 149, 255);\">Fish</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> lives in unoccupied rooms.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener